  "prompt": "How long will it take for a mi 20000 mah power bank to be delivered if ordered from the official mi website?",
  "response": "The delivery time for a 20000 mAh Mi power bank from the official Mi website can vary based on several factors, including your location, the shipping method selected, and any current promotions or events that may affect shipping times. Typically, standard shipping within the same country might take anywhere from 3 to 7 business days. For international shipping, it could take longer, potentially up to a few weeks.\n\nTo get the most accurate estimate, it's best to check the shipping details provided at the time of purchase on the official Mi website or contact their customer service directly.",
